{"tid":2512908,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【哲學】如果我有份幫銀河帝國起死星,咁我係唔係不道德?\"","createTime":"2021-05-02T06:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T06:55:55.000Z","uid":99762,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9a78647fc8d688eda4ac2fb86a025f7159902bed","tid":2512908,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"一個類比,希望大家一齊討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家銀河帝國將死星外判咗出去<br />\n而家要請人幫手起<br />\n人工高、福利好<br />\n但要幫手起的死星會被用黎鎮壓反抗軍<br />\n<br />\n我去做,咁我係咪不道德?"},{"pid":"38296dd0b4ae29117be0760773992b3955ee3e1e","tid":2512908,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:06:44.000Z","msg":"但係如果<br />\n我只係去起廁所之類的輔助設施,而唔係炮塔,蓄能之類,咁我係咪相對而言冇咁不道德?"},{"pid":"d220c20f3ff769a00509609b55293aab5a86e010","tid":2512908,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"又或者我十分之窮<br />\n需要呢份工,咁我迫於無耐去做呢？<br />\n咁我係咪不道德?"},{"pid":"b3766d5e017e20fdef0168cb4f72f96038f69e10","tid":2512908,"uid":373438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:08:37.000Z","msg":"樓主fg公務員？"},{"pid":"7528ccd08e4c40196fab4636cfe7934eaf367eba","tid":2512908,"uid":46720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:13:28.000Z","msg":"你自己都有咁多前設<br />\nE.G 迫於無耐去做,只係去起輔助設施<br />\n咁你心入面都有個答案<br />\n即使人地同你講係都好<br />\n你應該都係會去做架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3df5936671c9b235f0796628a1c8e3a56a12bb9","tid":2512908,"uid":103936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:16:09.000Z","msg":"一個類比,希望大家一齊討論<br />\n<br />\n樓主老母生左樓主出黎<br />\n樓主又走去幫手起死星<br />\n樓主老母係咪不道德?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c871cce7e1c6bf793bf6b9e37deaf4c1c3ff0145","tid":2512908,"uid":67116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:17:25.000Z","msg":"你唔做 第二個人上囉<br />\n製造武器係用黎殺人架啦"},{"pid":"06608d8aea370b91bccd8607a534559afc05bda